<h1>Welcome to the SimBreviloquent Plugin Demo</h1>

<p>
    This webpage is a <strong>simulator of a simulator</strong>, designed to demonstrate how the <strong>SimBreviloquent
        plugin</strong> for X-Plane 12 works within the simulator environment.
</p>

<p>
    The SimBreviloquent plugin allows users to download detailed flight dispatch information directly from <a
        href="https://www.simbrief.com" target="_blank">SimBrief</a>, provided they enter their SimBrief alias.
</p>

<p>
    This demo showcases the plugin's functionality, enabling you to experience how it behaves in a simulated
    environment.
</p>

<h2>Features of the SimBreviloquent Plugin</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Download flight dispatch information from SimBrief.</li>
    <li>Display sections of the dispatch information in separate windows.</li>
    <li>Group dispatch details into a comprehensive briefing preview window.</li>
</ul>

<p>
    Use this demo to explore the plugin's capabilities and see how it integrates seamlessly with X-Plane 12 to enhance
    your flight simulation experience.
</p>

<p>
    To get started, navigate through the menus above and explore the features of the SimBreviloquent plugin.
</p>
